{"_id":"xlhcnbXUPnqwPvXX","name":"Tier 1 Melee Critical Hits (Levels 1-4)","description":"Critical hit effects for melee attacks at Tier 1 (Levels 1-4). Effects are relatively mild for novice adventurers.","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-slashing-red.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"ZFFvmKjXpCvLxoku","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical strike deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":25,"range":[1,25],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"DwHyGhGXN6p7va4R","type":0,"text":"Rattled - The jarring impact throws off your foe's concentration. They have disadvantage on their next ability check.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":8,"range":[26,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"ability.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Rattled","duration":0}}},{"_id":"WlFduj8ImAL30MjE","type":0,"text":"Painful Strike - The searing pain gnaws at your foe's focus. They have disadvantage on concentration saves until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"concentration","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Painful Strike","duration":1}}},{"_id":"UglZg5OQ256F4OLJ","type":0,"text":"Ringing Skull - Your blow slams against their head and leaves their ears ringing. They are deafened until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[41,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"GhVVYNEdcv7XDdUx","type":0,"text":"Armor Dent - Your strike dents a plate of the target's armor. They take -1 AC until they spend an action to bend it back into shape.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-1,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"NgWc3OyKF7yL5Zkr","type":0,"text":"Disorienting Hit - Your blow leaves the target seeing stars. They have disadvantage on their next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Disoriented","duration":0}}},{"_id":"T3HHg7lSifxuIcnu","type":0,"text":"Dazed - Your devastating hit leaves your target reeling. They have disadvantage on their next attack roll.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Dazed","duration":0}}},{"_id":"mILCUC2OibtbdFr9","type":0,"text":"Knockdown - The force of your blow sends your target sprawling. They are knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"0P1I4KxTQHXKlRVU","type":0,"text":"Crippled Arm - Your strike mangles the muscles of their weapon arm. They take -2 to attack rolls until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"VdjVfK0cgxmKAHSv","type":0,"text":"Shield Sundered - Your strike splinters the target's shield or buckles their armor. They take -2 AC until it is repaired with Mending or smith's tools.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":4,"range":[75,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"z8SnwUaWnWJ2lmiq","type":0,"text":"Follow-Through - Your perfect follow-through opens the way for another blow. You have advantage on your next melee attack against the target.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.mwak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Follow-Through","duration":0}}},{"_id":"V9VXPvEf8MvG4Imk","type":0,"text":"Driving Slam - You drive your full weight into the blow. The target must succeed on a DC 11 Strength save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"7W6nMb3hwaFPyUqA","type":0,"text":"Bleeding Wound - Your strike opens a nasty gash that bleeds freely. The target takes an extra weapon die of damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"0jHK41aIJNbBgFOo","type":0,"text":"Perfect Strike - A masterful blow that fills your foe with dread. The target is frightened of you until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"H0hcl7ZkoryL3I5s","type":0,"text":"Blood in the Eyes - Your blow splashes blood across the target's face. They are blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"qbkPEV5qPdT6KWp1","type":0,"text":"Exposed Weakness - Your keen eye spots an opening in the target's guard. Attacks against them have advantage until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Weakness","duration":1}}},{"_id":"Ns1T8TMNQuvUaruy","type":0,"text":"Gut Wound - Your blade tears into the target's belly. They must succeed on a DC 11 Constitution save or be poisoned until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned","duration":-1}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":1,"attackType":"melee","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392745,"modifiedTime":1783703392745,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"RHGFEajZSAX1WEIm","name":"Tier 1 Melee Fumbles (Levels 1-4)","description":"Fumble effects for melee attacks at Tier 1 (Levels 1-4). Effects are relatively mild for novice adventurers.","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-slashing-red.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"b9Or7SaYvYeYzEFH","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - You stumble slightly but recover quickly with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":25,"range":[1,25],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"2P9vcaNFt2wrwqtb","type":0,"text":"Weapon Notched - Your blade chips against something hard. You take a -1 penalty to attack rolls until the weapon is repaired.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[26,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-1,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"FuxyFB0LHnF5Jufy","type":0,"text":"Jarred Wrist - You jar your wrist on the botched swing, taking a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"RDNCgtDRUM8xsQu3","type":0,"text":"Off Your Feet - You lurch off balance and have disadvantage on your next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":7,"range":[41,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Off Your Feet","duration":0}}},{"_id":"YivmNRLp3YfwyEd8","type":0,"text":"Off Balance - Your wild swing throws you off balance, giving you disadvantage on your next attack roll.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Off Balance","duration":0}}},{"_id":"nF1hdxgLJEVuRXAg","type":0,"text":"Dropped Guard - You drop your guard, taking a -2 penalty to your AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"h1uYqSSFFeo06KsZ","type":0,"text":"Overextended - You overreach and leave yourself open. The next attack against you has advantage.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Overextended","duration":0}}},{"_id":"BJWkLhOR4o7GQgII","type":0,"text":"Weapon Slipped - Your weapon slips in your grip. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Weapon Slipped","duration":1}}},{"_id":"DqxBoxFEzTBjjPHN","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Attack - Your clumsy swing telegraphs your intent. The target has advantage on its next saving throw against you.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed","duration":0}}},{"_id":"3M3ds6mMIPUyMmN3","type":0,"text":"Cut Yourself - The blade bites you on the backswing. You take one weapon die of damage to yourself.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[75,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"PEdBt6X7Q46xyocF","type":0,"text":"Sprawled - You trip over your own feet and fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"uPPxrhgjFdYb1h34","type":0,"text":"Wrenched Shoulder - You wrench your shoulder on the miss. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Wrenched Shoulder","duration":1}}},{"_id":"XYRrLVX5bHmJIbiI","type":0,"text":"Wide Open - Your reckless attack leaves you wide open. Attacks against you have advantage until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Wide Open","duration":1}}},{"_id":"jT18Iz8MSHV1rnUQ","type":0,"text":"Rattled - Your fumble rattles your nerve. You are frightened until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"gQ4q1ZabBf2F5cJ4","type":0,"text":"Weapon Dropped - Your weapon flies from your grasp and lands out of reach.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disarm"}}},{"_id":"Zvj33dKc2x2ISHXq","type":0,"text":"Tangled - You tangle in your own straps and gear. You are grappled until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"grappled","duration":1}}},{"_id":"Xd7eWKGqonQTMqvj","type":0,"text":"Wild Overswing - You overcommit disastrously. Make a DC 11 Dexterity saving throw or take 1d6 slashing damage and fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"slashing"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":1,"attackType":"melee","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392745,"modifiedTime":1783703392745,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"uXFSAopQmAgbcMd8","name":"Tier 1 Ranged Critical Hits (Levels 1-4)","description":"Critical hit effects for ranged attacks at Tier 1 (Levels 1-4). Effects are relatively mild for novice adventurers.","img":"icons/weapons/bows/longbow-recurve-brown.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"Fa60kcMVgj4WxKLb","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical strike deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":25,"range":[1,25],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"DZTzGgaK4ESY22AS","type":0,"text":"Rattled Target - Your shot startles the target, giving them disadvantage on their next ability check.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":8,"range":[26,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"ability.all","effectName":"Rattled","duration":0}}},{"_id":"d3IrGYDKbz52VS1q","type":0,"text":"Eye Threat - The projectile whistles past the target's eyes, giving them disadvantage on their next ranged attack.","img":"icons/svg/eye.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rwak","effectName":"Eye Threat","duration":0}}},{"_id":"zLOGZJOGpaVt7p6b","type":0,"text":"Muffled Ears - The shot clips the side of the target's head, leaving them deafened until the wound is treated.","img":"icons/svg/silenced.svg","weight":7,"range":[41,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"eiJARJAo6lO7UUIl","type":0,"text":"Distracting Shot - Your shot forces the target to focus on dodging, giving them disadvantage on their next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","effectName":"Distracted","duration":0}}},{"_id":"OztVH06IkLkDUGu9","type":0,"text":"Severed Tendon - Your shot severs a tendon in the target's arm, giving them -2 to attack rolls until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"B5UM1IG5lRwtalBH","type":0,"text":"Armor Piercing - Your shot finds a seam in the target's armor, imposing -1 AC until they take an action to reset it.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-1,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"r9b80477tIt2Uzt1","type":0,"text":"Suppressing Shot - A burst of covering fire breaks the target's nerve, giving them disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Suppressed","duration":1}}},{"_id":"op8MRd9phVrVLfwU","type":0,"text":"Grit in the Eye - A spray of grit and blood catches the target across the eyes, leaving them blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"z1plFcsOplIgOaiw","type":0,"text":"Exposed Target - Your shot forces the target to flinch open, granting advantage on attacks against them until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":4,"range":[75,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Target","duration":1}}},{"_id":"TpsQzILjwYQ2m486","type":0,"text":"Bleeding Wound - Your projectile leaves a deep gash, dealing an extra weapon die of damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"E96xRfqZCzO3goUp","type":0,"text":"Penetrating Shot - The projectile tears clean through muscle, dealing an extra 1d6 piercing damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"piercing"}}},{"_id":"Cfsvfd4f3VwSgeoz","type":0,"text":"Disarming Shot - Your projectile strikes the target's weapon hand, giving them disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","effectName":"Hand Struck","duration":1}}},{"_id":"49r66h6F91ryE8qr","type":0,"text":"Kneecapped - Your shot strikes the target's knee, forcing a DC 11 Dexterity save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone"}}},{"_id":"KTns2pcJzwdyZAht","type":0,"text":"Staggering Blow - The force of the shot staggers the target, forcing a DC 11 Strength save or take 1d6 bludgeoning damage as they are driven back.","img":"icons/svg/thrust.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"str","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"eFQiF06YQSy7V5D3","type":0,"text":"Punctured Lung - Your shot punctures a lung, forcing a DC 11 Constitution save or be poisoned while the target struggles to breathe.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned"}}},{"_id":"yadf6dIu3XqesIWA","type":0,"text":"Deadly Precision - A masterful shot lands with maximum weapon damage and leaves the target frightened of you until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":1}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":1,"attackType":"ranged","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392745,"modifiedTime":1783703392745,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"8MXoK3f2uwRM8vI8","name":"Tier 1 Ranged Fumbles (Levels 1-4)","description":"Fumble effects for ranged attacks at Tier 1 (Levels 1-4). Effects are relatively mild for novice adventurers.","img":"icons/weapons/bows/longbow-recurve-brown.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"Uo1QuOzrFNIWYcP3","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your shot goes wide but you recover your composure with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":25,"range":[1,25],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"0XyXLfiAb9AV8EBM","type":0,"text":"Watering Eyes - Your eyes water from the effort and you have disadvantage on your next ability check.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[26,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"ability.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Watering Eyes","duration":0}}},{"_id":"gfv6tS7z9BgFs8uB","type":0,"text":"Flinch - You flinch at your own misfire and have disadvantage on your next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Flinch","duration":0}}},{"_id":"i1zcmoay8OYm2aIY","type":0,"text":"Fouled Aim - Your aim is thrown off and you have disadvantage on your next attack roll.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[41,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Fouled Aim","duration":0}}},{"_id":"ByKbJe1vYR4LT4qX","type":0,"text":"Snapped String - Your bowstring snaps taut awkwardly and you have disadvantage on ranged attacks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rwak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Snapped String","duration":1}}},{"_id":"z1EQuPKMj64Hp5hQ","type":0,"text":"Overdrawn - You overdraw and wrench your form, taking a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"cEowdYWpjA4JpAh5","type":0,"text":"Recoil Strain - The recoil wrenches your arm; take 1d4 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d4","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"Et3fbAyygsQygXWW","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Shot - You telegraph your shot and your target has advantage on its next saving throw against you.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed Shot","duration":0}}},{"_id":"aFZgjf378iW74lRj","type":0,"text":"Caught Flat - You are caught flat-footed; attacks against you have advantage until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Caught Flat","duration":1}}},{"_id":"NSIWon208QzRLemI","type":0,"text":"Exposed Flank - Your stance falls apart, leaving a -2 penalty to your AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":4,"range":[75,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"QlY2n2BTeE8K9eNy","type":0,"text":"Jammed Solid - Your weapon jams solid and you have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Jammed Solid","duration":1}}},{"_id":"jFyq2lxriQGV1mvj","type":0,"text":"Dropped Weapon - Your ranged weapon slips from your grasp and lands at your feet.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disarm"}}},{"_id":"ir52DKtMEmAePcWM","type":0,"text":"Off-Balance - You lose your footing; make a DC 11 Dexterity saving throw or fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"m9bgO3mle10AazFF","type":0,"text":"Winded - The strain knocks the wind from you; make a DC 11 Constitution saving throw or take 1d6 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"KPWwDpvj6kcHJlOg","type":0,"text":"Stinging Rebound - Your shot rebounds and stings you; take 1d6 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"ISalAVUtTTklQ3Hu","type":0,"text":"Blinded - Your snapped string lashes across your eyes; you are blinded until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":1}}},{"_id":"4MC6zNpHqoc0lagd","type":0,"text":"Self-Impaling Bolt - Your own projectile catches you; take 1d8 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d8","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":1,"attackType":"ranged","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392745,"modifiedTime":1783703392745,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"GJZ1oipJOQMEDiBK","name":"Tier 1 Spell Critical Hits (Levels 1-4)","description":"Critical hit effects for spell attacks at Tier 1 (Levels 1-4). Effects are relatively mild for novice adventurers.","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"Sy4SEYnAv7xLs8Ki","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical spell deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":25,"range":[1,25],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"gGnN67lu0WqMMhX4","type":0,"text":"Ringing Aura - A piercing arcane tone rings in the target's ears, leaving them deafened.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":8,"range":[26,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"BtM8g53hQ9tUAcaI","type":0,"text":"Spell Feedback - Your spell disrupts the target's concentration. If concentrating, they must make a concentration save with disadvantage.","img":"icons/svg/silenced.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"concentration","effectName":"Spell Feedback","duration":0}}},{"_id":"fnN6klsnxsADHkch","type":0,"text":"Mental Disruption - Your spell rattles the target's mind. They have disadvantage on their next ability check.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[41,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"ability.all","effectName":"Mental Disruption","duration":0}}},{"_id":"c8DHx9tlqJ11SYzw","type":0,"text":"Magical Overload - The target's senses are briefly overwhelmed. They have disadvantage on their next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","effectName":"Magical Overload","duration":0}}},{"_id":"dNetksTJ5cb2C2si","type":0,"text":"Dazzling Spell - Your spell produces a brilliant flash. The target has disadvantage on their next attack roll.","img":"icons/svg/light.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","effectName":"Dazzled","duration":0}}},{"_id":"jQwfyS8zNgKFRYXs","type":0,"text":"Arcane Burn - Your spell leaves lingering magical energy. Target takes 1d4 force damage at the start of their next turn.","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-yellow-orange.webp","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"4DBzSPMENQq3bnwy","type":0,"text":"Elemental Surge - Your spell's element flares. Add 1d6 damage of the spell's damage type.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1S","damageType":"spell"}}},{"_id":"7jnJpJOymnzEh65s","type":0,"text":"Hex of Frailty - A hex of frailty erodes the target's defenses, giving them a -2 penalty to AC until removed.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"e91l4qCw9ZvaFMFe","type":0,"text":"Arcane Amplification - Your magical power surges! Deal an additional 1d8 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[75,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"kqAUyPoqnk27zF5I","type":0,"text":"Concussive Blast - A concussive shockwave hammers the target; they must succeed on a DC 11 Strength save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"prone"}}},{"_id":"2wbRn497jCmUXsdZ","type":0,"text":"Withering Curse - A withering hex corrodes the target from within; they must succeed on a DC 11 Constitution save or be poisoned.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned"}}},{"_id":"crFRbBiJfowLgrBo","type":0,"text":"Searing Flash - A blinding burst of arcane light sears the target's eyes, leaving them blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"JZ5Ik3mWFyPomeIW","type":0,"text":"Mind Spike - A lance of psychic force stabs the target's mind; they must succeed on a DC 11 Wisdom save or be frightened of you.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened"}}},{"_id":"V35VHihBdS5Yjubt","type":0,"text":"Magical Knockdown - The force of your spell knocks the target prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"AWxNXEo4dW6KbsB1","type":0,"text":"Arcane Vulnerability - Your magic disrupts the target's defenses. Attacks against them have advantage until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Arcane Vulnerability","duration":1}}},{"_id":"2BXKJbNjJJ9zZINB","type":0,"text":"Perfect Casting - A masterful spell! Deal maximum spell damage instead of rolling, plus the target is frightened of you until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":1}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":1,"attackType":"spell","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392745,"modifiedTime":1783703392745,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"dDSVmc51wy2NitEM","name":"Tier 1 Spell Fumbles (Levels 1-4)","description":"Fumble effects for spell attacks at Tier 1 (Levels 1-4). Effects are relatively mild for novice adventurers.","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"FDp95VXC82czPXQB","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your spell fizzles harmlessly with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":25,"range":[1,25],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"vQQjcNXgCMpQyVt5","type":0,"text":"Grounded Magic - Your spell earths itself through your body. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[26,33],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Grounded Magic","duration":1}}},{"_id":"d9wndSltxF9YIPK7","type":0,"text":"Magical Feedback - The spell's energy rebounds slightly. Take 1d4 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":7,"range":[34,40],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d4","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"52jWDWAhVXUd69eB","type":0,"text":"Spell Recoil - The spell lashes back as it leaves you. You have disadvantage on your next ranged spell attack.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":7,"range":[41,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rsak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Spell Recoil","duration":0}}},{"_id":"iAr5DtHw7QQt6pxg","type":0,"text":"Arcane Hiccup - Your magic stutters and misfires. You have disadvantage on spell attacks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.msak","attack.rsak"],"advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Arcane Hiccup","duration":1}}},{"_id":"mbMz7HKX86c2edBQ","type":0,"text":"Somatic Cramp - Your casting hand cramps violently. You have disadvantage on concentration checks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"concentration","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Somatic Cramp","duration":1}}},{"_id":"9d4cV2j1EYTu6mWk","type":0,"text":"Arcane Backlash - Raw magic rebounds into you. Take force damage equal to one of the spell's damage dice.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"PTXCt0tlqDUyX1SW","type":0,"text":"Component Combustion - Your material components ignite in your grip. Take 1d6 fire damage.","img":"icons/svg/fire.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"fire"}}},{"_id":"oSlyMPKCsJIY3cgb","type":0,"text":"Arcane Spark - Loose magic crackles across your skin. Take 1d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"MSdOE9lwtHfqVGXf","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Magic - Your fumbled casting tips your hand. Enemies have advantage on their next saving throw against your spells.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":4,"range":[75,78],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed Magic","duration":0}}},{"_id":"OL1E7xilSflOQSFr","type":0,"text":"Exposed Weave - Your botched weave leaves you unguarded. Attacks against you have advantage until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":4,"range":[79,82],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Weave","duration":1}}},{"_id":"HJgNM5zDV8Hg9Fv4","type":0,"text":"Warped Focus - The recoil throws off your aim. You take a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":4,"range":[83,86],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"Q3GjDjBjBTr81Zq1","type":0,"text":"Shattered Wards - The backlash shreds your protective wards. You take a -2 penalty to AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":4,"range":[87,90],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"vgHrMmDMU0uQXYRR","type":0,"text":"Backlash Sprawl - The detonation throws you off your feet. You are knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":3,"range":[91,93],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"R1aH3HZjpMEOHm2x","type":0,"text":"Deafening Boom - The spell erupts with a deafening crack. You are deafened.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":3,"range":[94,96],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"JxDxr4NMQuPFjfBk","type":0,"text":"Blinding Feedback - A blinding flash of misfired magic sears your eyes. You are blinded until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":2,"range":[97,98],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"q6ngY5XF4KvDaBa6","type":0,"text":"Catastrophic Rebound - Your spell collapses inward. Make a DC 11 Constitution saving throw or take 2d6 force damage and be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":2,"range":[99,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":11,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"force","effectCondition":"prone","failEffect":"Take force damage and be knocked prone"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":1,"attackType":"spell","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392745,"modifiedTime":1783703392745,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}